	"description": "In this article, I&#x27;ll discuss how we reached young audiences by combining\nrobotics with e-sports.\n\nWhat on Earth?\nEver heard of anything like it before? Me neither. The robot was created as part\nof Futurice [https://www.futurice.com/]’s project with Yle [https://yle.fi/],\nthe national broadcast company of Finland. \n\nYle produces content for TV, radio, and the web. It has a broad reach of older\naudiences, but has had trouble reaching younger ones. The goal of this project\nwas to use new technolog",
